import React from 'react'
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import { Container, Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap"

export const DosageDogs = () => {

  let email = " ";
  let password = " ";
  let grams = 0;
  let ml = 0;

  return (
    <>
      <Container className='contA'>
        <Form className="rounded p-4 p-sm-3">

          <Row className="rowD">
            <Col>
              <Form.Select aria-label="Default select example">
                <option>How much food you need based on your dogs weight ?</option>
                <option value="1">5kg = 100g</option>
                <option value="2">10kg = 200g</option>
                <option value="3">15kg = 280g</option>
              </Form.Select>
            </Col>

            <Col>
              <Form.Select aria-label="Default select example">
                <option>How much water you need based on your dogs weight ?</option>
                <option value="1">5kg = 350ml</option>
                <option value="2">10kg = 700ml</option>
                <option value="3">15kg = 1400ml</option>
              </Form.Select>
            </Col>
          </Row>

          <Row>
            <Col>
              <Form.Select aria-label="Default select example">
                <option>On how much portions you want to split your dosage ? </option>
                <option value="2">2</option>
                <option value="3">3</option>
                <option value="4">4</option>
              </Form.Select>
            </Col>
          </Row>

          <Row>
            <Col style={{ textAlign: 'center', display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
              <Button variant="outline-success" type="submit" size='lg'>
                Submit
              </Button>
            </Col>
          </Row>
          <Row>
            <Col style={{ textAlign: 'center', display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center' }}>
              <Button href="/" variant="secondary" size='lg'>
                Home
              </Button>
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Form>
      </Container>
    </>

  );
}
